patthana15.74:1.1_0: Saraṇaṁ saṅkiliṭṭhasaṅkilesikaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca nasaraṇo nasaṅkiliṭṭhasaṅkilesiko dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana15.74:2.1_0: Araṇaṁ asaṅkiliṭṭhasaṅkilesikaṁ dhammaṁ paccayā naaraṇo naasaṅkiliṭṭhasaṅkilesiko dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
